Neil Hamilton (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Neil_Hamilton_(actor) 0 James Neil Hamilton (September 9, 1899 – September 24, 1984) was an American stage, film and television actor, best known for his role as Commissioner Gordon on the Batman TV series of the 1960s.
